          <br />
          <div class = "col-md-3"></div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Questions? Comments? Contact Us!</h2>
            <br />
            
            <p> soorajb@mit.edu     |     rarnott@mit.edu        |     rodmy@mit.edu </p>
            <br />
            
            <h5> Made with &hearts; by the CLOSER team </h5>
